1.title: The Troublemaking Phantom Thieves

episode of.title: Kaitou Sentai Lupinranger vs. Keisatsu Sentai Patranger (TV Series 2018–2019)

1.plot: The Inter-dimensional Crime Group Gangler is using the items of the elusive Lupin Collection to attack Earth, but Kairi Yano, Toma Yoimachi and Umika Hayami are three mysterious thieves who stand up against them as the Lupinrangers, with the objective of stealing the collection back from their hands.

2.title: International Police, Chase After Them

episode of.title: Kaitou Sentai Lupinranger vs. Keisatsu Sentai Patranger (TV Series 2018–2019)

2.plot: The Lupinrangers encounter the three policemen who have the ability to transform into the Patrangers. For the possession of the Lupin Collection, a three-way battle between the thieves, the cops and Gangler begins.

3.title: Take Them Back No Matter What

episode of.title: Kaitou Sentai Lupinranger vs. Keisatsu Sentai Patranger (TV Series 2018–2019)

3.plot: The Patrangers make a stop at Bistrot Jurer which happens to be the Lupinrangers' hideout. The Lupinrangers then decide to take the opportunity and attempt to steal their VS Changers.

4.title: Unacceptable Relationship

episode of.title: Kaitou Sentai Lupinranger vs. Keisatsu Sentai Patranger (TV Series 2018–2019)

4.plot: The Patrangers investigate mysterious disappearances occurring in closed rooms and a stuffed animal is the only clue they have.

5.title: Targeted, the International Police

episode of.title: Kaitou Sentai Lupinranger vs. Keisatsu Sentai Patranger (TV Series 2018–2019)

5.plot: When the Patrangers get their hands on two new VS Vehicles, the Lupinrangers and Gangler step in to fight them for their possession.

6.title: What to Protect

episode of.title: Kaitou Sentai Lupinranger vs. Keisatsu Sentai Patranger (TV Series 2018–2019)

6.plot: Keiichiro is upset about his defeat to Lupin Red and is eager for a rematch, but his companions step in to remember him where his heart should be.

7.title: Always Saved

episode of.title: Kaitou Sentai Lupinranger vs. Keisatsu Sentai Patranger (TV Series 2018–2019)

7.plot: Umika has a date with Sakuya, who is oblivious to her true identity, while Kairi and Toma are in dire straits.

8.title: The Thieves' Identities

episode of.title: Kaitou Sentai Lupinranger vs. Keisatsu Sentai Patranger (TV Series 2018–2019)

episode of.title: Kaitou Sentai Lupinranger vs. Keisatsu Sentai Patranger (TV Series 2018–2019)

imdb.plot outline: The Lupin Collection, a vast ensemble of dangerous items acquired by the legendary gentleman thief Arsène Lupin, was stolen by an interdimensional crime syndicate known as Gangler. The Gangler receive opposition from two Super Sentai teams: one being the Lupinrangers who aim to steal back the collection to not only live up their namesake's reputation but also wish back those they have lost. The other team are Patrangers, tasked to uphold justice by retrieving the collection and taking down the members of Gangler. Both teams fight not only the Gangler, but each other, in order to collect the pieces of the Lupin Collection.
